    {

      "Normalization step is finished in adata.X\n",

      "Scale step is finished in adata.X\n",
      "PCA is done! Generated in adata.obsm['X_pca'], adata.uns['pca'] and adata.varm['PCs']\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "st.pp.filter_genes(data,min_cells=0.00*data.n_vars)\n",
    "st.pp.normalize_total(data)\n",
    "st.pp.log1p(data)\n",
    "st.pp.scale(data)\n",
    "st.em.run_pca(data,n_comps=50)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 2.2. add morphology information"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 3,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "The morphology feature is added to adata.obsm['X_morphology']!\n",
      "The data adjusted by morphology is added to adata.obsm['X_pca_morphology']\n",
      "Created k-Nearest-Neighbor graph in adata.uns['neighbors'] \n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "st.pp.tiling(data,out_path=\"./temp_tiling\",crop_size=40)\n",
    "st.pp.extract_feature(data)\n",
    "st.spatial.morphology.adjust(data,use_data='X_pca',radius=50,method=\"mean\")\n",
    "st.pp.neighbors(data,n_neighbors=25,use_rep='X_pca_morphology')"
   ]
  },
